00:05:53.569 --> 00:05:55.850
And also what is the order of priority?

00:05:55.850 --> 00:05:59.089
Well, obviously Jehovah is the first priority.

00:05:59.089 --> 00:06:02.410
And then generally we put love of neighbor ahead of our self

00:06:02.410 --> 00:06:05.490
because we consider our neighbor superior to us

00:06:05.490 --> 00:06:07.490
another principle.

00:06:07.490 --> 00:06:12.290
But you notice this says love your neighbor as your self.

00:06:12.290 --> 00:06:15.170
So that means there may be times when we have to weigh

00:06:15.170 --> 00:06:19.170
how this affects me a little bit ahead of my neighbor.

00:06:20.370 --> 00:06:25.050
Love Jehovah, love my neighbor, love myself.

00:06:25.050 --> 00:06:27.930
So how does doing this or not doing this?

00:06:27.930 --> 00:06:32.009
So how do these options reflect on my relationship

00:06:32.009 --> 00:06:34.610
with Jehovah or affect my relationship with Jehovah?

00:06:34.610 --> 00:06:39.370
