00:06:39.370 --> 00:06:41.370
How does doing this or not doing this

00:06:41.370 --> 00:06:43.610
or these options affect my neighbor?

00:06:43.610 --> 00:06:46.730
Who are my neighbors that are affected by this decision?

00:06:46.730 --> 00:06:51.449
Remembering that our closest neighbor is our family members.

00:06:51.449 --> 00:06:55.689
How does doing this or not doing this affect me?

00:06:55.689 --> 00:06:58.970
So as a test, I encourage you to take whatever decision,

00:06:58.970 --> 00:07:03.209
whatever situation that you may be struggling with right now

00:07:03.209 --> 00:07:07.569
and prayerfully use this principle as a starting point.

00:07:07.569 --> 00:07:10.970
And you may be amazed at the clarity it gives you

00:07:10.970 --> 00:07:15.089
and the other principles that it opens up to guide you.

00:07:15.089 --> 00:07:16.730
Well, what's the point?

00:07:16.730 --> 00:07:20.730
The point is that principles can help us make decisions

00:07:20.730 --> 00:07:23.089
