00:07:23.089 --> 00:07:25.730
But we need spiritual maturity.

00:07:25.730 --> 00:07:29.769
And frankly, now is the time that we have to grow

00:07:29.769 --> 00:07:32.810
to spiritual maturity so that we can make decisions

00:07:32.810 --> 00:07:34.970
based on Bible principles.

